---
description: Cursor-only models for orchestrator workflows; no external LLM CLIs.
alwaysApply: true
---

When following **cursor-orchestrator** commands: use **only** models selectable in Cursor (Chat / Agent). Map roles to tiers **A (strongest)**, **B (balanced)**, **C (fast)** per the plugin README. Never invoke `codex` CLI, raw provider scripts, or non-Cursor binaries for generation. Infrastructure CLIs (`br`, `bv`, `git`, agent-mail) are allowed.
